# CPListItem.AssistantCellPosition

**Enumeration**

Constants to specify the position of the assistant cell.

## Declaration

```swift
enum AssistantCellPosition
```

## Controlling the Assistant Cell Position

- **CPListItem.AssistantCellPosition.bottom**: Positions the assistant cell at the bottom of all visible cells.
- **CPListItem.AssistantCellPosition.top**: Positions the assistant cell at the top of all visible cells.

## Initializers

- **init(rawValue:)**

## Managing the Assistant Cell

- **CPListItem.AssistantCellVisibility**: Constants to specify the visibility of the assistant cell.
